data.description: This home boasts large spacious bedrooms and a finished 3 car garage. A large living room perfect for family movie nights. Open plan with vaulted ceiling, kitchen island so everyone can visit while preparing a meal or entertaining. Bright and cheery with large windows to allow the sunshine in plus an extended patio to enjoy spring and summer activities You can park your RV and have the convenience of a plug in on its own breaker. Schedule your showing today and don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to call it home!
